metadata.name: Moira
metadata.description:
1/1 Artwork Created By Saviz Shalchian.
Signed & Dated.
Unlockable Content:
Custom sized 1/1 physical mixed media print signed and dated.
(Free worldwide shipping).

Exploration of a visual representation of a portal to another dimension. In the center of the canvas, there is an abstract and swirling circle filled with colours and textures, illuminated with sparks of orange sunset. An image of strange and fantastic figure emanating from the circle, and floating in the air, representing the exotic denizens of this unknown dimension. There is a mysterious aura of beauty and adventure coming from this place, inviting the viewer to enter this unknown realm and explore its secrets.
